/--
A monoidal natural transformation is a natural transformation between (lax) monoidal functors
additionally satisfying:
`F.Œº X Y ‚â´ app (X ‚äó Y) = (app X ‚äó app Y) ‚â´ G.Œº X Y`
-/
@[ext]
